    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d honestly think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it shows\u2014the interior is spotless and the paint still has that perfect factory shine. It drives like a total dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
