    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1988 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2 is a superlative example of air-cooled engineering, featuring the desirable Getrag G50 five-speed transaxle for superior shift precision. The numbers-matching 3.2-liter flat-six engine remains in peak factory configuration, utilizing Bosch Motronic engine management for crisp, linear power delivery. The chassis is anchored by a flawlessly preserved torsion bar suspension and genuine staggered Fuchs alloys, ensuring the communicative handling dynamics the G-body is legendary for. With zero evidence of oil seepage, a pristine top-end, and a fully documented service history, this vehicle offers a turnkey experience for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
